responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "ECF30097453C99E43AD099AE0300AC3F", "If you have the time, I suggest an exploration of Carphin. I suspect you can uncover their doings there and any connection to the goblins. Be warned! That area is not for the faint of heart. We have lost many a scholar there in our desire to research the wreckage. Just in case you do not know of the location, I shall add it to your map.")
